    "type": "htmlSlide",
    "htmlContent": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"tr\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Vahiy ve Tebliğ Afişi</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap');\n\n        /* --- GENEL AYARLAR --- */\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);\n            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;\n            color: #fff;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        /* --- MASAÜSTÜ VARSAYILAN (Sabit & Ölçeklenebilir) --- */\n        #main-wrapper {\n            width: 100vw;\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            overflow: hidden; /* Masaüstünde scroll yok, sığdırma var */\n        }\n\n        .poster-container {\n            /* Sabit Orijinal Boyutlar */\n            width: 1500px;\n            height: 850px;\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n            \n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border: 4px solid #fbbf24;\n            border-radius: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            \n            /* Ölçekleme için merkez noktası */\n            transform-origin: center center;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease-out;\n        }\n\n        /* --- İÇERİK STİLLERİ (Masaüstü) --- */\n        .decoration {\n            position: absolute;\n            opacity: 0.07;\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            color: #fbbf24;\n            z-index: 0;\n            font-size: 220px;\n        }\n        .dec-top { top: -50px; left: 15%; content: \"VAHİY\"; }\n        .dec-bottom { bottom: -50px; right: 15%; content: \"TEBLİĞ\"; }\n\n        .process-layer {\n            flex: 3;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            padding: 50px;\n            border-bottom: 3px dashed rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .node {\n            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);\n            border: 3px solid #93c5fd;\n            padding: 35px;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            width: 240px;\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n        .node-source { border-color: #fbbf24; }\n\n        .node h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.8rem; color: #fbbf24; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }\n        .node p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #cbd5e1; margin-top: 15px; }\n        .node-icon { font-size: 4rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px; }\n\n        .flow-arrow-container {\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin: 0 30px;\n            position: relative;\n            top: -20px;\n        }\n        .flow-arrow {\n            font-size: 4.5rem;\n            color: #93c5fd;\n            margin: 10px 0;\n        }\n        .action-title {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #fff;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            background: #1e3a8a;\n            padding: 8px 25px;\n            border-radius: 30px;\n            border: 2px solid #93c5fd;\n        }\n        .action-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: #cbd5e1; text-align: center; max-width: 200px; margin-top: 10px; }\n\n        .terms-layer {\n            flex: 2;\n            display: flex;\n            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .term-box {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 40px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            border-right: 2px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .term-box:last-child { border-right: none; }\n        \n        .term-title-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }\n        .term-arabic { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3.2rem; color: #fbbf24; display: block; }\n        .term-meaning { font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: bold; color: #fff; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; }\n        .term-desc { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #e2e8f0; max-width: 75%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 15px; line-height: 1.6; }\n\n\n        /* -----------------------------------------------------------\n           MOBİL MODU (Media Query)\n           Ekran 1024px'den darsa (Tablet Dik & Telefon) bu kurallar çalışır.\n        ----------------------------------------------------------- */\n        @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {\n            #main-wrapper {\n                height: auto; /* Yükseklik serbest */\n                display: block; /* Flex'i iptal et */\n                overflow-y: auto; /* Dikey scroll aç */\n                padding: 10px;\n            }\n\n            .poster-container {\n                /* Sabitliği iptal et, esnek yap */\n                width: 100%;\n                height: auto;\n                transform: none !important; /* JS ölçeklemesini iptal et */\n                margin-top: 0;\n                border-width: 2px;\n            }\n\n            /* Akış Yönünü Değiştir (Yatay -> Dikey) */\n            .process-layer {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                padding: 30px 20px;\n                gap: 20px;\n            }\n\n            /* Kutuları Ekrana Sığdır */\n            .node {\n                width: 90%;\n                max-width: 100%;\n                padding: 20px;\n                transform: none !important; /* Varsa inline style'ı ez */\n            }\n            .node h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; }\n            .node-icon { font-size: 3rem; }\n\n            /* Okları Döndür */\n            .flow-arrow-container {\n                margin: 10px 0;\n                top: 0;\n            }\n            .flow-arrow {\n                transform: rotate(90deg); /* Aşağı baktır */\n                font-size: 3rem;\n                margin: 5px 0;\n            }\n            .action-title { font-size: 1.1rem; }\n\n            /* Alt Katmanı Düzenle */\n            .terms-layer {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                border-top: 2px dashed rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2);\n            }\n            .term-box {\n                border-right: none;\n                border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n                padding: 30px 20px;\n            }\n            .term-arabic { font-size: 2.5rem; }\n            .term-meaning { font-size: 1.8rem; }\n            .term-desc { font-size: 1rem; max-width: 100%; }\n\n            /* Arka plan süslerini küçült */\n            .decoration { font-size: 100px; opacity: 0.05; }\n            .dec-top { top: 10px; left: 10px; }\n            .dec-bottom { bottom: 10px; right: 10px; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <div id=\"main-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"poster-container\" id=\"poster\">\n            <div class=\"decoration dec-top\">VAHİY</div>\n            <div class=\"decoration dec-bottom\">TEBLİĞ</div>\n\n            <div class=\"process-layer\">\n                <!-- Kaynak -->\n                <div class=\"node node-source\">\n                    <span class=\"node-icon\">✨</span>\n                    <h3>ALLAH (cc)</h3>\n                    <p>Emir ve Hükümlerin Kaynağı</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Ok 1 -->\n                <div class=\"flow-arrow-container\">\n                    <div class=\"action-title\">VAHİY</div>\n                    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">➔</div>\n                    <div class=\"action-desc\">Allah'ın hükümlerini bildirmesi.</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Merkez -->\n                <div class=\"node\" style=\"transform: scale(1.15); border-color: #fff;\">\n                    <span class=\"node-icon\">🤲</span>\n                    <h3 style=\"color:#fff;\">PEYGAMBERLER</h3>\n                    <p>Vahyi alan ve ileten seçilmiş elçiler.</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Ok 2 -->\n                <div class=\"flow-arrow-container\">\n                    <div class=\"action-title\">TEBLİĞ</div>\n                    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">➔</div>\n                    <div class=\"action-desc\">Peygamberlerin vahyi iletmesi.</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Hedef -->\n                <div class=\"node\">\n                    <span class=\"node-icon\">👥</span>\n                    <h3>İNSANLAR</h3>\n                    <p>Mesajın muhatapları.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"terms-layer\">\n                <div class=\"term-box\">\n                     <div class=\"term-title-group\">\n                        <span class=\"term-arabic\">Resul</span>\n                        <span class=\"term-meaning\">\"ELÇİ\"</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"term-desc\">Kur'an-ı Kerim'de peygamberler için kullanılan, risalet (elçilik) görevini vurgulayan kavram.</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"term-box\">\n                    <div class=\"term-title-group\">\n                        <span class=\"term-arabic\">Nebi</span>\n                        <span class=\"term-meaning\">\"HABERCİ\"</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"term-desc\">Allah'tan aldığı haberleri (nübüvvet) insanlara ulaştıran kişi anlamındaki kavram.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- MASAÜSTÜ İÇİN ÖLÇEKLEME SCRİPTİ -->\n    <script>\n        function fitPoster() {\n            // Sadece masaüstü modunda çalış (Genişlik > 1024px)\n            if (window.innerWidth > 1024) {\n                const poster = document.getElementById('poster');\n                const winWidth = window.innerWidth;\n                const winHeight = window.innerHeight;\n                \n                // Orijinal boyutlar\n                const targetWidth = 1540; \n                const targetHeight = 890;\n\n                // Ölçek oranını hesapla\n                const scale = Math.min(winWidth / targetWidth, winHeight / targetHeight);\n                \n                // Uygula\n                poster.style.transform = `scale(${scale})`;\n            } else {\n                // Mobildeysek ölçeklemeyi temizle (CSS devreye girsin)\n                document.getElementById('poster').style.transform = 'none';\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Yüklenince ve yeniden boyutlandırılınca çalıştır\n        window.addEventListener('load', fitPoster);\n        window.addEventListener('resize', fitPoster);\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
    "title": "İnteraktif Sunum"
  },
  {
    "title": "Peygamberlerin Özellikleri",
    "content": "<ul><li>Peygamberler, güvenilir, dürüst, akıllı, zeki ve sabırlı insanlardır.</li><li>Günah işlemekten uzak dururlar ve topluma örnek olurlar.</li></ul>",
